section.t:
Several scenarios can cause a need for re-authentication and re-authorization:
        
									When a user changes the group that he/she wishes to attach to;
									When a user changes the access router used for connection (e.g., wireless roaming);
									When a user changes the medium used for physical connectivity (e.g., cellular to wireless, etc.).

